OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fshowers will slowly fade to leave a
OL,7,Flargely dry night, with variable
OL,8,Famounts of cloud and occasional clear
OL,9,Fspells. Turning increasingly cloudy
OL,10,Ffrom the south by dawn. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cloudy start with some light
OL,13,Fshowers. Cloud breaking to give some
OL,14,Fbright or sunny spells into the
OL,15,Fafternoon but with further showers,
OL,16,Flocally heavy. Feeling warm in
OL,17,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
