OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FSaturday, bright start but showers
OL,7,Fdeveloping later. Warm. A band of rain
OL,8,Fclearing south early on Sunday, with
OL,9,Fbrighter skies following. Further
OL,10,Fshowers Monday. Often breezy and
OL,11,Ffeeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
